column5: Just wanted to know if the ice condition in the bay of Quinty are still good was going to try it out Monday and Tuesday.

all depends on where your fishing id stay away from any high current area 2 quads and 1 lad on foot fell through yesterday,thank god all got out safe but i still can't figure why they all want to fish on 3" of ice in high current areas with this mild spell were having,when there tons of good eyes under my feet and i standing on 13" of ice.  taker easy and stay safe  Hawg Hunter
